{"article_id":"NEPXkqWUevlqjhHk","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"St. Louis Prosecutor Robert McCulloch announced Monday night","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"that a grand jury declined to indict officer Darren Wilson , 28 , for firing six shots in an August confrontation","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"that killed 18-year-old Michael Brown .","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"Here are the latest developments :","depth":2},{"id":4,"text":"Darren Wilson speaks about altercation :","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"On Tuesday , Ferguson police officer Darren Wilson sat down with ABC News ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"speaking publicly for the first time on the shooting death of Michael Brown .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"He described his side of the altercation ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"that Brown did not have his hands up","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"when he was fatally shot .","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"President Obama talks down `` destructive '' behavior :","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Speaking from Chicago at a scheduled immigration event ,","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"Obama condemned the `` destructive '' behavior","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"that caused fires , gunfire and destroyed property .","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"He also noted the many peaceful protests throughout the country ,","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"saying","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"he stands with them .","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"Gov . Nixon addresses safety going forward :","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"In a press conference alongside National Guard and law enforcement leaders , Missouri 's governor promised to deploy more than 2,200 troops","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"to keep peace in Ferguson .","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"Ferguson mayor criticizes National Guard :","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"Mayor James Knowles called out the National Guard for slow response speed ,","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"saying","depth":14},{"id":24,"text":"they did not deploy quickly enough","depth":15},{"id":25,"text":"to prevent violence and arson in the wake of a grand jury 's decision .","depth":15},{"id":26,"text":"He said","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"the Guard troops ,","depth":17},{"id":28,"text":"who were under the supervision of the unified command ,","depth":17},{"id":29,"text":"were available","depth":16},{"id":30,"text":"but were not deployed","depth":16},{"id":31,"text":"when city officials asked .","depth":16},{"id":32,"text":"Wilson speaks publicly for the first time :","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Officer Darren Wilson will speaking with ABC 's George Stephanopoulos on World News Tonight at 6:30 p.m . ET .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"It will be the first time","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"he has spoken publicly since the shooting on Aug. 9 .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Family comes out swinging :","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Benjamin Crump , a lawyer","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"representing Michael Brown 's family ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"blasted the prosecutor","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"who handled the grand jury .","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"`` We object as publicly and loudly","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"as we can","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"on behalf Michael Brown Jr. 's family","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"that this process is broken .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"The process should be indicted . ''","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"What we 're learning :","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"The pages and pages of grand jury documents are full of detail","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"about what happened .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"Wilson told the grand jury","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"that Brown `` looked like a demon ''","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"and that the altercation was like `` fighting Hulk Hogan . ''","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"Here are photos from Darren Wilson 's medical exam after the shooting .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Here 's what he said , in his own words .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Police have been busy :","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"At a Tuesday news conference , authorities said","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"they had made 61 arrests ;","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"59 of those arrested were from the area .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"It 's taken `` 10,000 policemen '' to control the mayhem ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"said St. Louis County Police Chief Jon Belmar .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"`` What I 've seen tonight is probably worse than the worst night","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"we had in August . ''","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"Social media is still blowing up :","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Twitter reported","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"that more than 3.5 million tweets had been sent by midnight ET","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"after the decision was announced at about 9 p.m .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Here 's a look at what users are sharing on Twitter and Instagram .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Overnight in Ferguson :","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"The streets of Ferguson were calmer on Tuesday morning .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Police said","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"last night 29 people were arrested ,","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"two police cars were set on fire ,","depth":16},{"id":72,"text":"at least a dozen buildings were burning ,","depth":17},{"id":73,"text":"there was looting and rioting","depth":18},{"id":74,"text":"and one officer was shot","depth":19},{"id":75,"text":"( not seriously ) .","depth":19},{"id":76,"text":"Police used tear gas","depth":16},{"id":77,"text":"to disperse crowds .","depth":16},{"id":78,"text":"However , so far no deaths or serious injuries have been reported .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"Flight restrictions out of Lambert-St. Louis International Airport expired .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"At least 150 gunshots fired :","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"St. Louis County Police Chief Jon Belmar said at a 1:30 a.m. CT news conference","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"that at least a dozen buildings were burning","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"and at least 150 gunshots had been fired , none by police .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Darren Wilson thanks supporters :","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"In a letter","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"released to KSDK-TV in St. Louis ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"Wilson wrote to supporters ,","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"`` I would like to thank you all","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"for standing up for me during this stressful time .","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"Your support and dedication is amazing","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"and it is still hard to believe","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"that all of these people","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"that I have never met","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"are doing so much for me . ''","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"He did not mention Brown .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Wilson could still face civil rights charges","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"brought by the Justice Department","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"or a civil wrongful death lawsuit","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"filed by Brown 's parents .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Brown 's mother reacts :","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"The call from McCulloch 's office came shortly before the official announcement .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"Attorney Benjamin Crump nodded sadly","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"as he listened .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"A few seconds later , he delivered the news to Brown 's mother , Lesley McSpadden .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"She screamed","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"and sobbed .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"McCulloch ,","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"would be willing to meet with her .","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"McSpadden jumped to her feet","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"and wailed .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"`` I do want to meet with him right now , ''","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"McSpadden screamed .","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"`` What do you mean","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"no indictment ? ! ''","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"Read more on the family 's reaction here .","depth":5},{"id":117,"text":"Police officer shot during protests :","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"In a burglary","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"that may have been timed","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"to take advantage of law-enforcement focus elsewhere ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"a police officer was shot and a woman killed in a St. Louis suburb south of Ferguson , Mo. ,","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"and the suspect remains at large .","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"FAA issues no-fly zone :","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"The Federal Aviation Administration at 11:15 p.m . ET restricted flights into and out of Lambert International Airport in St. Louis","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"to `` provide a safe environment for law enforcement activities . ''","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"Protests turn violent in Ferguson :","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"Despite efforts by Brown 's family and civil rights activists ,","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"minutes after the ruling , violent protests erupted in Ferguson .","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"Demonstrators taunted police ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"shattered windows","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"and set fire to two St. Louis County police cars .","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"Scores of police officers ,","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"armed with riot gear ,","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"dispersed a crowd of about 300 with volley after volley of smoke bombs , pepper spray and bean bags .","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"Looters plundered a Walgreens and Autozone store ,","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"while a Little Casears pizza restaurant and local beauty shop were set ablaze .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"Peaceful protests take place in other cities :","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"Demonstrators reacted more peacefully in several other cities ,","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"including New York , Oakland , Philadelphia , Detroit and Washington , D.C .","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"In New York , hundreds marched to Times Square","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"chanting ,","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"`` No justice , no peace , no racist police , ''","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"and carrying signs","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"that read ,","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"`` Jail Killing Cops ''","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"and `` Resistance Is Justified . ''","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"Protesters in Oakland , Calif. , laid in the middle of an intersection in silent protest ,","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"then marched down Broadway","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"shouting ,","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"`` Hands up , do n't shoot , ''","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"and `` Black lives matter","depth":15},{"id":152,"text":"-","depth":15},{"id":153,"text":"all lives matter . ''","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"Obama urges calm :","depth":6},{"id":155,"text":"In a nearly 10-minute statement in the White House press room after the ruling , President Obama said ,","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"`` We are a nation","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"built on the rule of law . ''","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"`` We need to accept","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"this decision was the grand jury 's to make . ''","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"later adding ,","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"`` We need to recognize","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"that the situation in Ferguson speaks to the broader problems","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"that we still face as a nation . ''","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":329,"left":167,"right":328,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":167,"left":0,"right":166,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":166,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":328,"left":3,"right":327,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":327,"left":279